siness value at the center of everything that you do.\n• You continuously strive for perfection and improvement, but you can clearly prioritize your development areas based on the environment in which you operate. You love to learn and recognize that there is always room to grow your skills and broaden your impact.\n• You have experience running and structuring continuous product discovery, specifically focusing on using customer research. You are an expert in examining your discovery findings within the business context and prioritizing based on highest value fastest delivery method.\n• You are a confident and competent product leader with excellent communication skills (both verbal and written) who can create the right narratives and share your ideas with all stakeholders (regardless of the level) and your immediate team.\n\nOUR OFFER:\n• Chance to work with highly skilled multi-national team of technology enthusiasts.\n• High level of flexibility and work-life balance – hybrid office model.\n• State-of-the-art equipment of your choice.\n• Direct and global impact on shaping the next generation of engagement and sports data technology services.\n• Investment in your continued professional development.\n\nAdditional Information\n\nSportradar is an Equal Opportunity Employer. We are committed to encourage diversity within our teams. All qualified applicants will receive consideration without regard to among other things, your background, status, or personal preferences'
